        "team": "T001"
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "user": "U001",
        "text": "The updated payer_rules.xlsx is live in the shared drive. UnitedHealthcare timely filing changed from 90 to 180 days effective March 15. All other payers unchanged.",
